AGI - After a "night spent quiet", Pope Francis "follows therapy and respiratory physiotherapy". It makes the Vatican press room known. After waking up, Bergoglio "did breakfast" and "regularly reads newspapers". The same sources exclude for today a second briefing with doctors, "it has not yet been calendarized" but for today "it is difficult". From the Gemelli Hospital Pope Francis continues to work. Today the bulletin of the Holy See Press Office publishes the message of the Pontiff to participants in the course for those responsible for the episcopal liturgical celebrations of the Pontifical Athenaeum Sant'Anselmo. "Dal Policlinico 'Gemelli', 26 February 2025". &nbsp;
Meanwhile, the office of the liturgical celebrations of pontifical makes known that it will be Cardinal Angelo De Donatis, Major Penitentiary and delegate of Pope Francis to preside, on the day of the beginning of Lent, the celebration, in the form of the Roman "Stations" at 16:30, in the church of Sant'Anselmo at the Aventine. Liturgy to which will follow the penitential procession towards the Basilica of Santa Sabina.
&nbsp;
<div </div
