Beginning of Lent is Wednesday 5 March. The office of liturgical celebrations warns that the cardinals, the archbishops, the bishops, the Benedictine monks and the Dominican fathers, who intend to participate in the celebration, "they are prayed to be in the church of Sant'Anselmo, wearing their own choral dress". &nbsp;
